      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.basel-kadem": [
          "7.\tWith this chain of narrators, from Ahmad bin Muhammed, from Muhammed bin Isa, from Abdullah bin Umar bin Hammad al-Ansari, that he ascribed it, saying: Abu Abdillah, peace be upon him, said: A man’s seek to cause harmony in his land is from (the trait of) manliness."
